text: Claude Carlin (born 17 January 1961) is a French former cyclist. He competed at the 1984 Summer Olympics and the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:French male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of France Category:Cyclists at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:People from Argentan Category:Sportspeople from Orne
